    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dash, bash, and race through wild arenas in a colorful action party game! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play solo or with friends in action-packed modes full of karts, jetpacks, and crystal-chasing fun.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ready. Set. Dash!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into <i>Chasers Dash &amp; Bash</i> - a playful, pick-up-and-play competition where every match is full of colorful action, surprising strategies, and fun for all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo or with friends, dash through obstacle courses, steal crystals, soar through the sky, and turn the tide with power-up items. It’s all about clever plays, quick moves, and lighthearted mischief.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/58807a38ba4dbf08134723958796223d.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=684 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/58807a38ba4dbf08134723958796223d.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/58807a38ba4dbf08134723958796223d.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a mix of modes that keep matches fresh, exciting, and unpredictable:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>Triathlon Race</strong> – Run, drive, and fly in multi-part obstacle races</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Battle Royale</strong> – Be the last Chaser standing! Outlast everyone in a shrinking arena</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>Crystal Chase</strong> – Steal and collect as a team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏈 <strong>Touchdown</strong> – Carry the crystal to the end zone</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Classic Battle</strong> – Mayhem in its purest form</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 <strong>Practice Stages</strong> – Hone your skills in 3 special maps</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/f1989cde3fdd5461c3604bbf36d09ca3.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/f1989cde3fdd5461c3604bbf36d09ca3.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/f1989cde3fdd5461c3604bbf36d09ca3.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grand Cups</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the heart of the competition in the Grand Cups, a multi-stage challenge to earn trophies and climb to the top. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/cde8c72ba0633c0cef484d7233e539b9.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/cde8c72ba0633c0cef484d7233e539b9.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/cde8c72ba0633c0cef484d7233e539b9.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Power-Up Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up one item in each hand and make your move!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blast, block, and bounce your way to victory with tools that reward timing and creativity - from rolling beetles to tricky traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/5251546d9b208a78f6e375b760aa28c0.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=684 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/5251546d9b208a78f6e375b760aa28c0.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/5251546d9b208a78f6e375b760aa28c0.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Move Your Way</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, drive, or fly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop into karts, buses, jetpacks, or flying devices to chase shortcuts and surprise your rivals. And  give your teammate a lift… or catch one yourself! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/0148ffd280e680837584045abde3ac50.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=684 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/0148ffd280e680837584045abde3ac50.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/0148ffd280e680837584045abde3ac50.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Extra</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect XP to unlock new stages, climb the leaderboard, and discover 12 fully-voiced characters, each with multiple skins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/ed66ee9c067ea18986757893cd787a02.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=684 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/ed66ee9c067ea18986757893cd787a02.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/ed66ee9c067ea18986757893cd787a02.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plus: Split Screen &amp; Online Play</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the fun to the couch or the world stage.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to <strong>12-player matches</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split screen</strong> for up to 4 players (even online!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stage voting, team selection, and plenty of laughs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for family nights, parties, or friendly rivalries</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/b7b5764621457c3147b0dd2184d11a22.poster.avif?t=1759355120\" width=480 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/b7b5764621457c3147b0dd2184d11a22.webm?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375650/extras/b7b5764621457c3147b0dd2184d11a22.mp4?t=1759355120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
